00:02:13.457 --> 00:02:14.793
My head had cleared up,

00:02:14.817 --> 00:02:17.944
but my body was still
too weak to fight back,

00:02:17.968 --> 00:02:20.302
and the pain was blinding.

00:02:20.765 --> 00:02:22.848
I thought I'd be severed in two.

00:02:23.804 --> 00:02:25.379
In order to stay sane,

00:02:25.403 --> 00:02:28.677
I silently counted the seconds
on my alarm clock.

00:02:29.622 --> 00:02:31.357
And ever since that night,

00:02:31.381 --> 00:02:37.155
I've known that there are 7,200
seconds in two hours.

00:02:39.140 --> 00:02:42.378
Despite limping for days
and crying for weeks,

00:02:42.402 --> 00:02:46.808
