about rape like I'd seen on TV.

00:02:47.361 --> 00:02:49.382
Tom wasn't an armed lunatic;

00:02:49.406 --> 00:02:51.169
he was my boyfriend.

00:02:51.193 --> 00:02:53.802
And it didn't happen in a seedy alleyway,

00:02:53.826 --> 00:02:55.887
