from being raped that night,

00:03:37.058 --> 00:03:39.200
and it wasn't my skirt,

00:03:39.224 --> 00:03:41.174
it wasn't my smile,

00:03:41.198 --> 00:03:43.394
it wasn't my childish trust.

00:03:43.832 --> 00:03:47.566
The only thing that could've stopped me
from being raped that night

00:03:47.590 --> 00:03:49.640
is the man who raped me --

00:03:49.664 --> 00:03:51.677
