00:06:37.735 --> 00:06:40.302
and headed straight
for a nervous breakdown.

00:06:41.098 --> 00:06:44.722
My self-worth was buried
under a soul-crushing load of silence

00:06:44.746 --> 00:06:48.038
that isolated me from everyone
that I cared about,

00:06:48.062 --> 00:06:50.967
and I was consumed
with misplaced hatred and anger

00:06:50.991 --> 00:06:52.755
that I took out on myself.

00:06:53.635 --> 00:06:56.245
One day, I stormed out
of the door in tears

00:06:56.269 --> 00:06:58.212
after a fight with a loved one,

00:06:58.236 --> 00:06:59.935
