00:11:44.471 --> 00:11:47.391
(Laughter)

00:11:47.415 --> 00:11:50.620
At times, our search
for understanding in Cape Town

00:11:50.644 --> 00:11:52.811
felt like an impossible quest,

00:11:52.835 --> 00:11:54.934
and all I wanted to do was to give up

00:11:54.958 --> 00:11:57.174
and go home to my loving
husband, Vidir,

00:11:57.198 --> 00:11:58.409
and our son.

00:11:59.994 --> 00:12:02.357
But despite our difficulties,

00:12:02.381 --> 00:12:07.009
